</p>
</clause>
<clause id="_recommended_value_of_the_frequency" obligation="normative"><title>Recommended value <eref type="inline" bibitemid="ci2015" citeas="[1]"/> of the frequency</title><p id="_1fb44bd2-6802-4532-9980-7435d5608201"><stem type="MathML"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>f</mi></math></stem>(Yb<sup>+</sup>, quadrupole) <stem type="MathML"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>=</mo><mn>688358979309308.3</mn><mo rspace="thickmathspace">&#8290;</mo><mrow xref="U_NISTu31"><mi mathvariant="normal">Hz</mi></mrow>









